data.description:
Welcome to this charming Craftsman-style home that effortlessly blends classic design with modern amenities. This beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence offers a warm and inviting atmosphere, with an open kitchen and living area, updated wood like tile flooring, and a spacious covered patio, making it a perfect place to call home. Located on a quiet cul de sac with amazing neighborhood amenities, featuring pond, splash pad, playground and pavilion.
As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the craftsmanship and attention to detail that defines this home. The open concept living area features large windows that flood the space with natural light, showcasing the elegant wood like tile flooring that runs throughout. The cozy living room flows seamlessly into the well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern appliances, plenty of counter space, and an island for casual dining.
This home boasts three generously sized bedrooms, each offering a tranquil retreat. A huge bonus is an ofice/study area.  The primary suite is a true sanctuary, with its own private en-suite bathroom and ample closet space. The two additional bedrooms share a beautifully updated bathroom.
One of the standout features of this property is the large covered patio, where you can enjoy outdoor gatherings year-round. The extended concrete patio offers additional space for outdoor seating and is ideal for entertaining. Whether you're savoring a morning cup of coffee or hosting a BBQ with friends, this outdoor space is sure to be a favorite spot.
For those seeking extra storage or a workshop, you'll be delighted to find a substantial outbuilding on the property with electricity, providing endless possibilities for hobbies and storage needs. Whether you're a DIY enthusiast or simply need more space for your belongings, this outbuilding is a valuable asset.
Seller will contribute $5,000 towards buyers rate buy down or closing costs.
